Name: QualityStandardName
Description: Name of the QualityStandard using the DDI Name structure.

Name: Label
Description: A display label for the QualityStandard. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the QualityStandard. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content.

Name: StandardUsed
Description: Provide the citation and location of the source published standard using the OtherMaterialType.

Name: ComplianceDefinition
Description: Provides a list of quality concepts in the quality standard.
